<h3 id="Books">Books</h3>
<span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Ilan_Berman&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5" title="Edit section: Books"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span>
